<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Herbal Knowledge Project</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <style>
    /* Global Styles */
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      color: #333;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* Header Section */
    header {
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px 0;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5em;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* Navbar Section */
    nav {
      background-color: #34495e;
      display: flex;
      padding: 10px 0;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin: 0 15px;
      font-size: 1.1em;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      background-color: #2ecc71;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    /* Hero Section */
    .hero {
      background-color: #2ecc71;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 100px 20px;  /* Increased padding for better visibility */
      flex-grow: 1; /* Takes up remaining space */
      height: 50vh; /* Ensures it takes half the viewport height */
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      background-image: url('https://example.com/your-plant-image.jpg'); /* Optional background image */
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 3.5em; /* Increased font size */
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.5em; /* Increased font size for readability */
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .hero .plant-icon {
      font-size: 5em; /* Increased icon size */
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    /* Content Section */
    .container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.4em;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #34495e;
    }

    .section {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #ecf0f1;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .section-icon {
      font-size: 2em;
      margin-right: 20px;
      color: #3498db;
    }

    .section-content h3 {
      font-size: 1.5em;
      color: #34495e;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .section-content p {
      font-size: 1.1em;
      color: #555;
    }

    /* Footer Section */
    footer {
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
    }

    footer p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #3498db;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
  <!-- Font Awesome for Icons -->
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Header Section -->
  <header>
    <h1 style="font-size: 200%;">Design and Development of a Large Language Model for Recognizing the Usage of Traditional Herbs</h1>
  </header>

  <!-- Navbar Section -->
  <nav>
    <a href="#abstract">Abstract</a>
    <a href="#introduction">Introduction</a>
    <a href="#problem">Problem Statement</a>
    <a style="border-right:1px solid white" href="#objectives">Objectives</a>
    <a href="/images">Images</a>
    <a href="/files">Files</a>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Herbal Knowledge Project</h1>
    <p>Preserving and Expanding Traditional Medicinal Wisdom with AI</p>
    <div class="plant-icon">
      <i class="fas fa-seedling"></i> <!-- Plant Icon -->
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <div class="container">
    <h2 id="abstract">Abstract</h2>
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-icon">
        <i class="fas fa-book-open"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="section-content">
        <h3>Abstract</h3>
        <p>The project aims to develop large language models specializing in herbs and traditional medicine, unifying scattered data from certified sources to create a cohesive knowledge base, while also addressing gaps in current resources.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 id="introduction">Introduction</h2>
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-icon">
        <i class="fas fa-laptop-code"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="section-content">
        <h3>Introduction</h3>
        <p>This project leverages AI technologies to preserve and enhance traditional medicinal knowledge, offering a unified, multilingual, and scalable knowledge base for herbal research and healthcare innovation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 id="problem">Problem Statement</h2>
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-icon">
        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="section-content">
        <h3>Problem Statement</h3>
        <p>Despite efforts by organizations like AYUSH, the knowledge of traditional medicinal herbs remains fragmented and inaccessible. AI technologies have not been effectively applied to integrate and expand this knowledge base.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 id="objectives">Objectives</h2>
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-icon">
        <i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="section-content">
        <h3>Objectives</h3>
        <p>The project seeks to collect, preprocess, and store multimodal data, train large language models, develop image-based question answering systems, and create user-friendly platforms for accessibility and research.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer Section -->
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 Herbal Knowledge Project. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>Contact us at: <a href="mailto:sskumar2k@gmail.com">sskumar2k@gmail.com</a></p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
